{"tid":1502877,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[MHW WORLD] 玩家心中玩法討論區","createTime":"2019-08-24T18:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T08:59:27.000Z","uid":144279,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15ff3e8176477e67d647184e82f0048b3bf36d3a","tid":1502877,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"Monster Hunter World(MHW)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okTsJMO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FokTsJMO.png&h=1515141d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係一款多人遊玩嘅遊戲玩家可以透過接取任務討伐不同怪物去獲取裝備 <br />\n<br />\n遊戲中有不同趣味玩法 例如釣魚 農場打埋等。<br />\n<br />\n但我個人打得多都覺得冇乜野好玩因為我發現作為一款多人合遊戲。缺乏好多趣味性遊戲多人合作玩法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我有一個想法</span><br />\n<br />\n就係狂㩒制嘅小遊戲<br />\n<br />\n圖片中我用咗速龍同速龍王做示範 因為速龍速龍王係遊戲中嘅經典怪物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2M2xHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2M2xHB.jpg&h=91339f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當怪物出現<br />\n<br />\n我地通常都會狂劈有時可以劈到佢地暈 但如果MHW官方可以加入小遊戲會點樣？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2SASJn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2SASJn.jpg&h=c65960ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩家係村中嘅小鋪頭買啲道具 利用道具兩人沖向怪物兩人向反方向跑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOHASJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOHASJO.png&h=7154ec02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透過玩家狂㨆o制儲捆綁度如果成功可以將其捆綁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxGaGCg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxGaGCg.png&h=3191c595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 如果MHW官方加入該操作大家會唔會玩得開心啲？<br />\n<br />\n我唔識日文唔知點比意見日本官方睇 有冇識日文嘅人幫我send比官方睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想知大家有冇其他小遊戲玩法一齊討論下？<br />\n<br />\n利申 所有圖都係上網搵"},{"pid":"48654ad020d6ea4b7b94bf173bbbf4b25858f4e3","tid":1502877,"uid":144279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"推